column1: Lester Adams, M.D. home movies -- Reel 1
column3: Fourth of July parade with minstrel show, old automobiles, people in costume. Closeup of minstrel players in blackface. Men, women, boys, and girls compete separately in races outdoors. Potato race, sack race, three-legged race, human wheelbarrow race. Closeups of winners follow each race. Tug of war competition. Patients in beds on balcony. Interior of dining room with people seated around large table. Boys and men in baseball uniforms pose outdoors. One jersey reads “Belmont.”
